<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Petition Page</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styles.css">


  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <!-- Header content goes here - i dont think i need one  -->
    </header>
    <main>
      <section class="petition">
        <h1>Support Our Cause</h1>
        <p>Lift the Ban and Let Our Cats Code!</p>
        <img src="/images/cat.png" alt="cat">

        <p>
          We, the undersigned, are writing to request the immediate unbanning of
          the Cats Code account on your platform. Cats Code is a valuable member
          of our online community, sharing valuable insights and knowledge on
          various programming topics. However, it has come to our attention that
          Cats Code has been unjustly banned from your platform. We believe in
          the importance of free speech and expression on the internet. By
          banning Cats Code, you are limiting the voices and perspectives that
          are represented on your platform. We urge you to reconsider your
          decision and reinstate Cats Code's account on your platform. Doing so
          will not only benefit the programming community but also uphold the
          principles of free speech and expression. Thank you for your attention
          to this matter.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section class="sign-petition">
        <h2>Sign the Petition</h2>
        <form id="petition-form">
          <label for="name">Full Name:</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required />

          <label for="city">City:</label>
          <input type="text" id="city" name="city" required />

          <label for="agree">I agree to sign this petition:</label>
          <input type="checkbox" id="agree" name="agree" required />

          <button type="submit">Submit</button>
        </form>
      </section>
      <section class="petition-signatures">
        <h2>Petition Signatures</h2>
        <table id="signature-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Name</th>
              <th>City</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
    </footer>
    <script>
      const petitionForm = document.querySelector("#petition-form");
      const signatureTable = document.querySelector("#signature-table");
      const signatureRows = signatureTable.querySelector("tbody");

      const signatures = [];

      petitionForm.addEventListener("submit", (event) => {
        event.preventDefault();

        const name = event.target.elements.name.value;
        const city = event.target.elements.city.value;
        const signature = { name, city };

        signatures.push(signature);

        signatureRows.innerHTML = signatures
          .map(
            (signature) =>
              `<tr><td>${signature.name}</td><td>${signature.city}</td></tr>`
          )
          .join("");
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>